# Zed keybindings

When the user asks about Zed editor keybindings, shortcuts, leader keys, or agent/thread panel bindings:

1. Read `~/.config/zed/KEYBINDINGS.md` for the human-readable reference.
2. Read `~/.config/zed/keymap.json` if they want exact config or something missing from the reference.
3. Leader key is `\` (backslash). Base keymap is Cursor on Linux.

Do not guess bindings — use those files as source of truth.
